Package: tezr
Title: Access the Turkiye's National Thesis Center Database
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R:
    person("Emrah", "Er", , "eer@eremrah.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Access the Turkiye's National Thesis Center (Ulusal Tez Merkezi)
    database at <https://tez.yok.gov.tr>. Search, retrieve, and analyze
    dissertation metadata from Turkish universities. Supports basic and
    advanced search, thesis details retrieval, lookup tables, and aggregate
    statistics.
